02:24.231 --> 02:26.232
Yeah!

02:35.242 --> 02:37.243
- It's a beautiful day, isn't it?
- Uh-huh.

03:03.145 --> 03:05.063
- Bye, Tonya.
- Bye.

03:15.908 --> 03:17.658
Clean up that mess, boy.

03:19.453 --> 03:20.953
- Pete, hungry?
- Huh?

03:21.121 --> 03:23.664
