03:31.757 --> 03:33.466
- Bye, girls.
- Bye, Daddy.

03:33.634 --> 03:35.426
Let's go, Max.

03:37.930 --> 03:40.473
Get in the house, pup. Harry Rex.

03:40.641 --> 03:44.644
All those weekends, fishing,
drinking, lounging...

03:44.812 --> 03:48.314
...opportunities lost
to do-it-yourself house renovations.

03:48.482 --> 03:51.651
- Tragic, just tragic, Jake.
- Yeah.

03:53.153 --> 03:55.029
Makes Carla happy, my man.

03:55.197 --> 03:58.241
Spent four marriages trying to figure out
what makes women happy.

03:58.409 --> 03:59.867
